ore":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T21:09:46.000Z","msg":"她用日文表示，自己已經「沒有辦法了」（仕方がない）<br />\n睇得太多日本悲劇文學?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956dde3f08acb8d10583f02ab27b0069b1412e79","tid":1010230,"uid":9681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2bf401cac5c6f5c711ae7847c4bd7d88f700b088","tid":1010230,"uid":208722,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"31b71197dc39699ecbc9321da39fb9ba39ae57fc","tid":1010230,"uid":59743,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"71adadc5e61ea7a4b24f97111a9c631aa3fa1a24","tid":1010230,"uid":208722,"like":52,"dislike":6,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T20:52:42.000Z","msg":"第一世界嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n左膠式嘅悲劇浪漫真係害死幾代歐美人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T20:59:16.000Z","msg":"原來係有 First World Problem 呢樣野,又學到野<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/18869\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F18869&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=d5497071\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/18869</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T21:00:47.000Z","msg":"飲飽食醉就會去煩更高層次嘅嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T22:13:14.000Z","msg":"冇論咩處境，人類就係有戇鳩問題要面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649eba81b513ceca29ee226e304f7202618ab488","tid":1010230,"uid":164387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T22:16:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9001881b4d0d593e6e9930bab6604dd3805a6aea","tid":1010230,"uid":22694,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T22:25:13.000Z","msg":"真係悶到先殺？<br />\n可能有精神病，抑鬱"},{"pid":"472f54c97e13230d28a5a4dcd9e0421c26c74f94","tid":1010230,"uid":132038,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T22:31:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3fc4c793690d8110a9355c419fbecf098762f60","tid":1010230,"uid":43041,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T22:36:34.000Z","msg":"無病呻吟<br />\n<br />\n仕方がない咁中二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f538ecbcef9b63938ef0c8ceca57d717825d1b35","tid":1010230,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T23:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71359f92df20e40b05357f975db1cc4ac96121f","tid":1010230,"uid":71913,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T23:37:31.000Z","msg":"會用日文 應該都係有d悲天憫人 中二病<br />\n<br />\n咁佢要死都無辦法"},{"pid":"416c14f8f94df5219feddc4fb11bd262bfbd1e32","tid":1010230,"uid":17103,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T23:45:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">她表示，自己看起來人生美滿（great life on paper），<strong>品嚐過多數人吃不起的美食，可以消遙自在地旅遊，又曾在美國最好的兩個城巿居住過，但形容自己對這一切已感到毫無意義</strong>（trivial）：「我與至親至愛共處時，經常感到疏離；我經歷人生高低起跌，也亳無感覺；我明白到，這是第一世界的終極問題。」她強調沒有單一事件，觸發她輕生。</span><br />\n<br />\n無錯 ... 細過咩到做過, 好撚多 friends 日日出去蒲去 wet 去威. 家下睇返對自己完全無咩改變過, 除左洗鳩晒 D 錢.<br />\n<br />\n食好野? 一兩個鐘就完, 之後又係變屎<br />\n去旅行? 一兩個星期後又返返現實做野賺錢<br />\n買靚車? 每日幾多分鐘留係車到? 重要怕花怕撞<br />\n屌個閪? 16 - 40 都試過 ... 屌完都唔知為乜 ...<br />\n<br />\n不過諗唔通就會走左去自殺, 諗得通就會安排點係死前過得舒服 D (聽落消極, 其實非常正面)<br />\n<br />\n我見好多人要排頭, 其實佢地心入面寂寞到極點靠呢 D 外在既野慰藉自己.  識人係搵球半一年, 1/5 時間係旅行, 但係佢個樣完全唔係享受."},{"pid":"c1ab3adb2106edb9d6b7fd51e7fb65e3dd9eb565","tid":1010230,"uid":119896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T23:48:15.000Z","msg":"R.I.P."},{"pid":"60756fc99e9ff495894055462913a4c973bc5aed","tid":1010230,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2455d91209b4691702f92c2be4b9ee32e0cee7d","tid":1010230,"uid":200199,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T20:57:09.000Z","msg":"一個人冇目標/嗜好會好易有情緒病"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T23:51:09.000Z","msg":"港女都無，所以好多有公主病<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c5e6afccbe7608606afc6b78aeef7c40332e0e","tid":1010230,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T23:52:06.000Z","msg":"死都死得有條理"},{"pid":"b4dfb0c22865d102d409a721b436f23a75d86759","tid":1010230,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"71adadc5e61ea7a4b24f97111a9c631aa3fa1a24","tid":1010230,"uid":208722,"like":52,"dislike":6,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T20:52:42.000Z","msg":"第一世界嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n左膠式嘅悲劇浪漫真係害死幾代歐美人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T23:52:15.000Z","msg":"猶太人用嚟毁滅西方文明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d959eb68fd22c4c1837b38b5e5230ccfdd0774d","tid":1010230,"uid":22553,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T23:54:03.000Z","msg":"諗住死前，應該去下落後地區做下義工感受下先。又或者搵個安靜地方打坐冥想下，做咗唔得，最後先再揀死都未遲啦"},{"pid":"2e7aeea00cc25c47aec6252ccdffee35929bcec9","tid":1010230,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T00:03:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}